<DOCNO>WT15-B11-51</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA033-000677-B042-312</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/claremont/gsp/gsp49.htm 204.71.237.79 19970209185834 text/html 70986
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 18:59:12 GMT
