<P>
Savings: $0.218 million (GF)
<P>
<B>1110.  Abolish Animal Health Technician Examining Committee,
abolish Animal Health Technician Examining Committee Fund and
revert balance to General Fund</B>
<P>
Comments: In addition to the savings below, this would also save
$90,000 in permitting fees.
