Fund</B>
<P>
Comments: To the extent that worthwhile programs are funded through
this program, they should compete with other programs in the General
Fund.
<P>
Savings: $0.305 million (GF)
<P>
<B>3460.  Withdraw from Colorado River Board of California; redirect
