Fee Account and revert balances to the General Fund</B>
<P>
Comments: The Beverage Container Recycling Program is an economic
failure.  Economic recycling programs do not need to be mandated
and uneconomical ones should not be.  In addition to the savings
noted below, this reform would save $358,986,000 in annual taxes
and fees.
<P>
Savings:  $84.932 million (GF)
<P>
  
<P>
<B>3540.  Reduce positions for four land use coordinators in Department
of Forestry</B>
<P>
