<TITLE>Seattle Times 1996 TOC</TITLE>
<META name="description" content="1996 Columns Table of Contents">
<META name="keywords" content="FREE, Knight-Ridder, Seattle Times, Columns, Op-Eds, 1996">
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" BACKGROUND="/free/Images/bluewhite_paper.gif"><IMG SRC = "/free/Images/flogo.gif" ALT = "">
<P>Knight-Ridder Columns</P>
<TABLE CELLSPACING=2 CELLPADDING=1><CAPTION><H2>As appearing in the <CITE>Seattle Times</CITE></H2>
</CAPTION>
<UL>
<TR>
	<TD><LI><A HREF="Gift.ST1996.html">Economics Helping Santa</A></TD><TD>12/22/96</TD></TR>
<TR>
	<TD><LI><A HREF="Presidio.ST1996.html">Liberating National Parks from Political Dependency</A></TD><TD>12/11/96</TD></TR>
<TR>
	<TD><LI><A HREF="FishDem.ST1996.html">Democracies Don't Fight--Unless It's Over Fish</A></TD><TD>11/27/96</TD>
</TR><TR>
	<TD><LI><A HREF="Speech.ST1996.html">A Green Campaign Speech for a Better Environment</A></TD><TD>11/13/96</TD>
