<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/free/ST96/Gift.ST1996.html 204.71.237.79 19970209191214 text/html 6069
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 19:13:00 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 23-Jan-97 17:32:02 GMT
