<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/free/pubs/WSJ.wolf.html 204.71.237.79 19970209191555 text/html 7233
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 19:16:40 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:07:16 GMT
