William Rusher, Claremont Institute Senior Fellow; former Publisher of National Review<BR>
Marc Ryan, Waterbury Republican American editorial writer<BR>
Ted J. Smith III, Associate Professor of Mass Communications at Virginia Commonwealth University<BR>
R. Emmett Tyrrell Jr., Editor of The American Spectator<BR>
Dick Williams, Atlanta Journal columnist  <BR>
</blockquote>
</BODY>
